{"lemma":"راحَةُ","slug":"راحَةُ","root":"ر.#.ح","root_slug":"ر-_-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-_-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16989"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَاحَ (rāḥa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"recreation, leisure"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"comfort, ease"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ample space, wide room, a free space"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"palm of the hand"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *raḥat-, modified by the meaning of an ample or wide space of the above word."},"ipa":["/raː.ħa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16989","headword_ar":"رَاحَةٌ","root":"rwH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rest, repose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ease; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEabN","text_ar":"تَعَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cessation of trouble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inconvenience, and of toil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"freedom therefrom;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAisotiraAHapu","text_ar":"الاِسْتِرَاحَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A;) like ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHN","text_ar":"رَوَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned in the first paragraph as an inf. n. in a similar sense, as are also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHapN","text_ar":"رَوْحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHapN","text_ar":"رَوَاحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawiyHapN","text_ar":"رَوِيحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e., as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"experiencing relief from grief"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lifulaAnK fiY h`*aA AlA^amori mino rawaAHK","text_ar":"مَا لِفُلَانٍ فِى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ مِنْ رَوَاحٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapK","text_ar":"رَاحَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not, for such a one, in this affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"event, any rest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifoEalo","text_ar":"اِفْعَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*`lika fiY saraAHK wa rawaAHK","text_ar":"ذٰلِكَ فِى سَرَاحٍ وَ رَوَاحٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thou that in a state of ease"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and rest."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-  See also 4, near the middle of the paragraph.       -A2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wife;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EirosN","text_ar":"عِرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) because one trusts to her, or relies upon her, and becomes quiet, or easy, in mind. (TA.)       -A3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaf~N","text_ar":"كَفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or [rather] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm of the hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, MF;) for the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaf~","text_ar":"كَفّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"includes the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAHp","text_ar":"راحة"},{"kind":"text","text":"with the fingers: (MF:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHN","text_ar":"رَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, * Msb, K, *) [or rather this, said in the K to be syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHaAtN","text_ar":"رَاحَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is a coll. gen. n., of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.,] and [the pl. is]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHaAtN","text_ar":"رَاحَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaEuwhu","text_ar":"دَفَعُوهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlr~aAHi","text_ar":"بِالرَّاحِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They pushed him with the palms of the hands"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) The saying of a poet,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      A_i*aA dalakato $amosu Aln~ahaAri biraAHi"},{"kind":"text","text":"is explained as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When the sun of day has set, and men, looking towards it, shield themselves from its rays with the palms of their hands:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to IAar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sun of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"day has become dark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by reason of the dust of battle,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and it is as though it were setting, and people have found rest from its heat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraAHN","text_ar":"بَرَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brH","text_ar":"برح"},{"kind":"text","text":"; where other readings are mentioned.]) ―         -b2-  [Hence, app., as seems to be indicated in the TA,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapu Alkalobi","text_ar":"رَاحَةُ الكَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain plant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw Alr~aAHapi","text_ar":"ذُو الرَّاحَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sword of El-Mukhtár Ibn-Abee-' Obeyd"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Eth-Thakafee."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A court, an open area,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a yard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) of a house. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarakotuhu A^anoqaY mina Alr~aAHapi","text_ar":"تَرَكْتُهُ اَنْقَى مِنَ الرَّاحَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I left him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, more clear than the court, open area,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of a house,] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"than the palm of the hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) meaning, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without anything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b5-  And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHN","text_ar":"رَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Plain and open tracts of land, producing much herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, but comprising soft places and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAviym","text_ar":"جَرَاثِيم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jurovuwmapN","text_ar":"جُرْثُومَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not forming any part of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bed of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a torrent nor of a valley;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one whereof is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISh, K.) ―         -b6-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plicature"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a garment, or piece of cloth: (K, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"original plicature"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: so in the saying, in a trad., respecting a new garment, or piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiTowihi EalaY raAHatihi","text_ar":"اِطْوِهِ عَلَى رَاحَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fold thou it in the manner of its original plicature"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","MF","TA","ISh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}